<div class="faq">
  <h2>FAQ</h2>
  <h4>
    What is a bus stop id?
  </h4>
  <p>
    a bus stop id is a 7-digit code found on every bus stop sign (ex: "1000533").
  </p>
  <h4>
    How do I use this thing?
  </h4>
  <p>
    Enter your bus stop id in the text field and click the bus icon.
    The app will display which busses are coming, the time until their arrivals,
    the current weather at that stop, and a short forecast for the next hour.
  </p>
</div>
